       01  WS-PRES-POSTED            PIC X(7)   VALUE SPACES.
       01  WS-PRES-REJECT            PIC X(7)   VALUE SPACES.
       01  WS-PRES-REASONS           PIC X(40)  VALUE SPACES.
       01  WS-PRES-IDX               PIC 9(3)   VALUE 0.
       01  WS-PRES-FLD               PIC 9(1)   VALUE 0.
       01  WS-PRES-J                 PIC 9(3)   VALUE 0.
       01  WS-PRES-CH                PIC X(1)   VALUE SPACES.

       01  WS-CONN-FLAG              PIC X(1) VALUE "N".
           88  WS-CONNECTED                   VALUE "Y".

       EXEC SQL BEGIN DECLARE SECTION END-EXEC.
       01  HV-DB-NAME                PIC X(80).
